openMessageBrowserForClass: aBehavior selector: aSymbol editString: aString	"Create and schedule a message browser for the class, aBehavior, in 	which the argument, aString, contains characters to be edited in the text 	view. These characters are the source code for the message selector 	aSymbol."	| newBrowser |	(newBrowser _ Browser new) setClass: aBehavior selector: aSymbol.	^ Browser openBrowserView: (newBrowser openMessageEditString: aString)		label: newBrowser selectedClassOrMetaClassName , ' ' , newBrowser selectedMessageName